<TextStyle.Green>Dark of Night is a basic game server that removes most Tek (but not all) and adds several simple mods to create a closer to real life feel.</>

02/05/24 Added Brachiosaurus and Maewing to the server
1/14/24 Removed Tek, Adjusted several stack settings, Added Carchar
12/31 Server set to public
tab1.text2:
Wild dino max level = 200
Breeding 3X official
Harvest Rates 2X official

All other settings are to official servers
tab1.text3:
Server is 18 plus, however personal threats can result in admin action 
Distructive behavior is not allowed 
Normal Ark rules apply
